      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just never stops. the nerves, the burning... it's like being awake inside a fire 24/7. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting to exist when existing just means more pain. sometimes i look at the silence and think how much better it would just be to have that peace. permanent peace.",
